    "The first example in this notebook was translation of French into English, which we included as Figure 6 in the Appendix of this paper.",
    "We modified this code to save the output of the model, safety ratings, and the other values into a CSV.",
    "For our experiments, we used Gemini Pro 1.5 through API calls."
